<p>How do I allow user to reply at email and handle it? ( in term of php code et email configuration)</p>  <p>This process is used by many website to protect sender personnal infos :</p>  <ol> <li>User A write a private message in an HTML form.</li> <li><p>PHP send the message by email to user B with a random email address like <code>rEyoLdP-8946@mydomain.com</code></p></li> <li><p>User B reply to <code>rEyoLdP-8946@mydomain.com</code></p></li> <li>PHP somehow get the email and store the answer</li> </ol>